{"tid":1547299,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成立檔案資料庫","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:38:05.000Z","uid":289316,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0832b8e72527cc67cbb93f9b80547f357e33d393","tid":1547299,"uid":289316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"利申和理非。7月起一直聽劉細良節目。今晚繼續聽，佢有一個建議幾值得大家做，就係成立檔案資料庫，將d 警暴片段整理，擺入資料庫度，以供到時清算或者起訴警暴時用。以及紀錄證人口供資料，以證明被捕人士無辜，因為捉左到正式起訴都可能2年時間，到時可能會記憶冇咁清楚，對被捕者不利。<br />\n條片大約最後20分鐘左右有講點做。希望有能力既人士幫忙成立。thx all！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0qFWIWnxGcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0qFWIWnxGcw&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2qF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=ebe13aa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0qFWIWnxGcw</a>"},{"pid":"914f65a5037e605c19155dc3dc2869d8d7b35564","tid":1547299,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07f1b488f4bbcafc4d2ebd0067b6113e40f57dbf","tid":1547299,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ac426d8be15e2b69da701633c33a5c2fd52e9cf","tid":1547299,"uid":217704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf7d7bbd1cdcb2e9ee95dab241573df6b3db9e40","tid":1547299,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b744228